-# Features Section
%section.bg-gray-50.dark:bg-gray-800
  .py-8.px-4.mx-auto.max-w-screen-xl.sm:py-16.lg:px-6
    .max-w-screen-md.mb-8.lg:mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900.dark:text-white
        Designed for simplicity and efficiency
      %p.text-gray-500.sm:text-xl.dark:text-gray-400
        Our platform provides all the tools you need to streamline your tax preparation process, saving you time and reducing errors.
    .space-y-8.md:grid.md:grid-cols-2.lg:grid-cols-3.md:gap-12.md:space-y-0
      %div
        .flex.justify-center.items-center.mb-4.w-10.h-10.rounded-full.bg-primary-100.lg:h-12.lg:w-12.dark:bg-primary-900
          = heroicon "document-text", options: { class: "w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 lg:w-6 lg:h-6 dark:text-primary-300" }
        %h3.mb-2.text-xl.font-bold.dark:text-white
          Effortless Receipt Management
        %p.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Easily upload, categorize, and store all your receipts in one secure place. Never lose a deductible expense again.
      %div
        .flex.justify-center.items-center.mb-4.w-10.h-10.rounded-full.bg-primary-100.lg:h-12.lg:w-12.dark:bg-primary-900
          = heroicon "calculator", options: { class: "w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 lg:w-6 lg:h-6 dark:text-primary-300" }
        %h3.mb-2.text-xl.font-bold.dark:text-white
          Accurate Tax Calculations
        %p.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Our tools help you accurately calculate your tax obligations based on your income and deductions.
      %div
        .flex.justify-center.items-center.mb-4.w-10.h-10.rounded-full.bg-primary-100.lg:h-12.lg:w-12.dark:bg-primary-900
          = heroicon "lock-closed", options: { class: "w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 lg:w-6 lg:h-6 dark:text-primary-300" }
        %h3.mb-2.text-xl.font-bold.dark:text-white
          Secure Data Storage
        %p.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
          Your financial data is encrypted and stored securely, ensuring your privacy and peace of mind.
